        <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #bed230;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">If you are using a drawing or selection tool and Auto-Adjust is enabled, you will not be able to use the tool outside of the true canvas. The cursor changes to a no symbol <img src="../../../Images/Capture/cursor_capture_no_symbol.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> to indicate areas outside of the true canvas boundaries where drawing and selection tools are disabled. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2,General.OnlineOnly">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Capture/Appearance/Resizing/Resizing-the-Canvas.htm">Resizing the Canvas</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
